{"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"getKeyMode"},{"kind":"text","text":"() -> "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@M@RFIDManager@objc(cs)RFIDResult","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"RFIDResult","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.rfid.RFIDManager\/documentation\/RFIDManager\/RFIDResult"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"content":[{"text":"Return Value","type":"heading","anchor":"return-value","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the fetch is successful, the data field of "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.rfid.RFIDManager\/documentation\/RFIDManager\/RFIDResult"},{"type":"text","text":" is Int."},{"type":"text","text":"\n"},{"type":"text","text":"如果获取成功，"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.rfid.RFIDManager\/documentation\/RFIDManager\/RFIDResult","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"的data字段为"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Int"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"English","anchor":"English"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The KeyMode parameter controls the trigger mode of the device’s scan key.","type":"text"},{"text":"\n","type":"text"},{"text":"When KeyMode = 0, the key value 1 will be returned in the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"keyUpBlock"},{"type":"text","text":" callback of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"RFIDBleManager.shared.setKeyEvent"},{"type":"text","text":" when the scan key is lifted;"},{"type":"text","text":"\n"},{"type":"text","text":"When KeyMode = 1, the key value 3 will be returned in the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"keyDownBlock"},{"type":"text","text":" callback of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"RFIDBleManager.shared.setKeyEvent"},{"type":"text","text":" when the scan key is pressed, and